When I read the file and then write it back out, PowerShell mangles the JSON.

Here's my code:

```
$infile = "C:\input.json"
$outfile = "C:\output.json"
$data = ConvertFrom-Json -InputObject (Get-Content -Raw $infile)
Set-Content $outfile ($data | ConvertTo-Json)
```
